<p><b>Donald G. Firesmith</b> (born June 14, 1952) is an American <a href="/wiki/Software_engineer" title="Software engineer">software engineer</a>, consultant, and trainer at the <a href="/wiki/Software_Engineering_Institute" title="Software Engineering Institute">Software Engineering Institute</a> (SEI).</p>
<p></p>
