<li id="cite_note-12"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-12">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Donald Firesmith with Peter Capell, Dietrich Falkenthal, Charles B. Hammons, DeWitt T. Latimer IV, and Tom Merendino, <i>The Method Framework for Engineering System Architectures</i>, Auerbach Publication, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781420085754" class="internal mw-magiclink-isbn">ISBN 978-1-4200-8575-4</a>, 2008, pp. 51–61</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-13"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sei.cmu.edu/library/assets/mfesatutorialoneday20090420.pdf"><i>Method Framework for Engineering System Architectures (MFESA)</i></a>, tutorial at the 2009 System and Software Technology Conference (SSTC'2009), April 2009. Retrieved 2009-09-23.</span></li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/f/Firesmith:Donald.html">List of publications from the DBLP Bibliography Server</a> Retrieved 2009-09-23.</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
